<td><span class="location">The <a href="/wiki/Ardennes" title="Ardennes">Ardennes</a>, <a href="/wiki/Belgium" title="Belgium">Belgium</a>, <a href="/wiki/Luxembourg" title="Luxembourg">Luxembourg</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Germany" title="Germany">Germany</a></span></td>
