<th colspan="2" style="background: lightsteelblue; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Strength</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;">840,000+ men <sup id="cite_ref-cirillo-53_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-cirillo-53-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>,<br />
424 medium tanks and <a href="/wiki/Tank_destroyers" title="Tank destroyers" class="mw-redirect">tank destroyers</a>,<br />
394 <a href="/wiki/Artillery" title="Artillery">artillery</a> guns</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;">500,000 men,<br />
500 medium tanks,<br />
1,900 artillery guns and <i><a href="/wiki/Nebelwerfers" title="Nebelwerfers" class="mw-redirect">Nebelwerfers</a></i></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background: lightsteelblue; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Casualties and losses</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;">American: 89,500<br />
(19,000 died,<br />
47,500 wounded,<br />
23,000 captured or missing)<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-dlink24591_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-dlink24591-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup>
<p>British: 1,408<br />
(~200 killed,<br />
~1,200<sup id="cite_ref-cirillo-53_0-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-cirillo-53-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> wounded or missing)<sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-3" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;">91,132 killed, wounded, captured or missing<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4" title=""><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
