<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;;background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Campaignbox_Western_Front_(World_War_II)" title="Template:Campaignbox Western Front (World War II)"><span title="View this template" style=";background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Campaignbox_Western_Front_(World_War_II)" title="Template talk:Campaignbox Western Front (World War II)"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Western_Front_(World_War_II)&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Western_Front_(World_War_II)&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";background: lightsteelblue; font-size: 90%;;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
</div>
<div style="padding: 0.2em 0; line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><a href="/wiki/Western_Front_(World_War_II)" title="Western Front (World War II)">Western Front</a></span></div>
</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px;">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
