</div>
</div>
<div class="infobox sisterproject">
<div class="floatleft"><a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Ardennes:_Battle_of_the_Bulge/Chapter_III" title="s:The Ardennes: Battle of the Bulge/Chapter III"><img alt="Wikisource" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/50px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png" width="50" height="52" border="0" /></a></div>
